text: Sharlene Natasha Whyte (born 19 May 1976) is an English actress. She is best known for portraying the roles of Jenny Edwards in the CBBC drama series The Story of Tracy Beaker and Adanna Lawal in the BBC school-based drama series Waterloo Road. As well as starring in various stage productions, she has also made appearances in television series such as Doctors, Casualty, Silent Witness, Coronation Street, Sadie J, We Hunt Together and Stephen. ==Biography== Whyte is of Grenadian descent. She trained at the Royal Academy of Dramatic Art from 1996 till 1999. ==Other websites== * Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:English stage actors Category:English movie actors Category:People from Nottingham
